{"tid":2052561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國最新導向：武漢肺炎可能起源東南亞地區","createTime":"2020-06-05T15:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T21:57:03.000Z","uid":3080,"like":30,"dislike":159,"uniUserReply":109,"replies":[{"pid":"c72263195d1be9ec1e1aa9c0bdc568b31ad77883","tid":2052561,"uid":3080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:29:36.000Z","msg":"太長廢事貼曬,反正大部分都係廢話<br />\n想研究就自己入去睇<br />\n我貼重點就算<br />\n<a href=\"https://view.inews.qq.com/k/20200605A0NWFY00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fview.inews.qq.com%2Fk%2F20200605A0NWFY00&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=a60709ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://view.inews.qq.com/k/20200605A0NWFY00</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6FiBdcf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6FiBdcf.png&h=f6e6bb52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.關於新冠狀病毒的起源，文章分析了中國所有已知的蝙蝠冠狀病毒，然後進行的地域分析，認為雲南等地是最接近新冠狀病毒的起源的地方，但是因為某些蝙蝠採樣涉及到了雲南與 東南亞的邊境地區，<span style=\"color: red;\">所以不排除緬甸，老撾，越南或其他東南亞國家地區的可能性</span>。<br />\n<br />\n 2.根據冠狀病毒的跨樣本感染情況以及進化情況的分析，有更確實的證據證明這個病毒具有大自然而不是實驗室。<br />\n 這與我以前幾篇文章中的推測非常接近，說病毒是實驗室造出來的人都是對生命科學沒什麼了解的人群。論文也再次驗證了我的另一個事實，病毒很可能是起源於東南亞 地區，尤其是中緬邊境以及越南，老撾等東南亞地區，<span style=\"color: red;\">其中的馬來菊頭蝠，很有可能是新冠病毒的起源</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而且我們這次也在廣東查貨的走私馬來穿山甲裡也找到了與新冠病毒基因相似度極高的穿山甲冠狀病毒</span>，到現在了還不能警醒一下嗎？"},{"pid":"583c8ccaf9b4a4db2df599225f0e899a5f8b9ecb","tid":2052561,"uid":226955,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:30:46.000Z","msg":"好悶呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7238c6d3a4af8816df6eca9639a677fd9c56c503","tid":2052561,"uid":25601,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:32:28.000Z","msg":"敵人唔夠多"},{"pid":"0e66be7a92f2089e91b618f2bb70f9fc70389c6d","tid":2052561,"uid":19252,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:33:55.000Z","msg":"可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾d信心啦，又要威又要戴頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d7e7e8ce4b29daa8e431f6cc2658465d95fe29","tid":2052561,"uid":62226,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:33:58.000Z","msg":"預防疾病嘅角度有啲意思，起碼知唔應該食蝙蝠，唔理佢邊度生活<br />\n但係喺追究人類錯誤上，冇咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fda2702397ecf3279d3aa273442cf675b19329","tid":2052561,"uid":338439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:35:16.000Z","msg":"八國聯軍不遠矣"},{"pid":"0e51bed175a81dacbaf4ccfbd3026fa2f0c92637","tid":2052561,"uid":4285,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:35:17.000Z","msg":"係啦，搵啲又窮又弱嘅國家食咗死貓佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9290135ed4b74089e5b09d2551dee6c21a875ef","tid":2052561,"uid":214173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:35:17.000Z","msg":"總之就唔係中國啦,佢都係想咁啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837fdd4590a967cca5a5b7fa3afca3c62ec207ee","tid":2052561,"uid":77196,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"89fda2702397ecf3279d3aa273442cf675b19329","tid":2052561,"uid":338439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:35:16.000Z","msg":"八國聯軍不遠矣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:35:39.000Z","msg":"百國聯軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3ed43c1c43d85a0baaea98a74662a5bb2eecf7","tid":2052561,"uid":219541,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:35:55.000Z","msg":"遲啲瀨埋北極<br />\n<br />\n愛基斯摩人或成病毒源頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f379c25f16a5891b5fd56c9511f3033a317c3f","tid":2052561,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:36:03.000Z","msg":"